title: Ibrahimovic's Sweden faces Denmark in Euros playoff derby
text: Photo: FREDRIK SANDBERG/TT, AP Sweden's Zlatan Ibrahimovic celebrates scoring the opening goal during the UEFA Euro 2016 group G qualifying soccer match between Sweden and Moldova at Friends Arena in Stockholm, Sweden, on Monday Oct. 12, 2015. (Fredrik Sandberg / TT via AP) SWEDEN OUT Sweden's Zlatan Ibrahimovic celebrates scoring the opening goal... NYON, Switzerland (AP) — Zlatan Ibrahimovic's Sweden will face Denmark in a Nordic derby in the Euro 2016 playoffs. Sweden's Zlatan Ibrahimovic celebrates scoring the opening goal during the UEFA Euro 2016 group G qualifying soccer match between Sweden and Moldova at Friends Arena in Stockholm, Sweden, on Monday Oct. 12, 2015.
